graph TD
    %% --- Initial Setup ---
    Start([User Submits UserMessage]) --> DisableInput[Disable Sending New Messages]
    DisableInput --> InputData[/Input: MainThread + UserMessage/]
    InputData --> BAML_Router{{BAML Function 1: Routing Analysis}}

    %% --- Routing Decision ---
    BAML_Router -- Outputs --> RIE[/RoutingInterfaceEvent\na: intent\nb: tool_call_needed\nc: tool_mode\nd: tool_name\ne: response_text/]
    RIE --> UI_InitialResponse[/UI: Show response_text/]
    UI_InitialResponse --> AppendRIE[Append RIE to MainThread]
    AppendRIE --> DecisionToolNeeded{tool_call_needed?}

    %% --- Path A: No Tool Needed ---
    DecisionToolNeeded -- False --> EnableInput[Enable Sending New Messages]
    EnableInput --> End([End Turn])

    %% --- Path B: Tool Needed (Orchestration) ---
    DecisionToolNeeded -- True --> ActivateSpinner[/UI: Show Spinner/Progress Indicator/]
    ActivateSpinner --> RouteOrchestrator[Route to Orchestrator based on 'tool_mode']
    RouteOrchestrator --> UI_InitTool[/UI: Show 'Initializing toolNamespace.toolName...'/]

    UI_InitTool --> OrchSetup[Orchestrator Setup:\nPrepare context, schema, intent, original message]
    OrchSetup --> BAML_Plan{{BAML Function 2: Tool Planning\n(Chain of Thought)}}

    %% --- Tool Execution Prep ---
    BAML_Plan -- Outputs --> ExecutionPlan[/Plan Data:\na: reasoning\nb: toolName\nc: Query/text/object\nd: description/]
    ExecutionPlan --> UI_ShowDesc[/UI: Update response_text with 'description'/]

    %% --- Tool Execution & Post-Processing ---
    UI_ShowDesc --> ExecuteTool[Execute Actual Tool\nusing Query/text/object]
    ExecuteTool -- Raw Output --> PostProcessing[Post-processing & Stats Extraction]

    PostProcessing -- Create --> ToolEventPack[/ToolEvent Package:\nStatus, Operation, Data, Stats,\nUserMsg, Intent, Reasoning, Description/]
    ToolEventPack --> UI_Preview[/UI: Show preview data stats/]

    %% --- Final Response Generation ---
    UI_Preview --> BAML_Response{{BAML Function 3: create{ToolName}Response\nTakes ToolEvent}}
    BAML_Response --> AddInternalThread[Add ToolEvent to internal {ToolNamespace}Thread]

    AddInternalThread --> UI_FinalResponse[/UI: Show Final Response as New Message\n(packaged with necessary data)/]
    UI_FinalResponse --> AppendFinalMain[Append ToolResponseEvent to MainThread]
    AppendFinalMain --> EnableInput
